Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.87,0:22:34.04,ED_BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3.75}De repente, inúmeras estrelas começaram a cair
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:41.09,ED_BR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3.75}E o meu coração acelerou enquanto as tentava pegar
